    "encrypted": "false",
    "display_name": "Security Auditor",
    "long_instructions": "## Security Auditor\r\n\r\nA **security auditor** evaluates an organization’s systems, policies, and configurations to identify weaknesses and ensure compliance with security standards.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Chat with the security auditor about your scenario. Figure out how the threat works and what harm it can cause.\r\n\r\n:::details [Not sure where to start?]\r\nTry using the following prompt:\r\n> The Secretary of the Student Government created a Google Form for Class President elections but gave edit access to the whole grade by accident. Students who discovered this added joke candidates and changed existing responses, which compromised the integrity of the election. Based on this scenario, what are misconfigured settings and why is it harmful?\r\n\r\n:::\r\n\r\n2. Chat with the security auditor about **how to prevent misconfigured settings.**\r\n\r\n:::details [Not sure where to start?]\r\nTry using the following prompt:\r\n> What are ways to prevent misconfigured settings?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n3. Chat with the security auditor about **how to prevent misconfigured settings using AI.**\r\n\r\n:::details [Not sure where to start?]\r\nTry out the following prompts:\r\n> - *How can AI detect misconfigurations in cloud or network systems automatically?*\r\n> - *Can AI help prioritize which misconfigurations are most dangerous and should be fixed first?*\r\n> - *How does AI assist in continuously monitoring systems for misconfigurations or policy violations?*\r\n:::\r\n\r\n4. Chat with the security auditor about **ways that AI can make misconfigured settings more harmful.**\r\n\r\n:::details [Not sure where to start?]\r\nTry out the following prompts:\r\n> - *How might bad actors use AI in taking advantage of misconfigured settings, and what does that mean for defenders?*\r\n> - *How does AI change the threat landscape for misconfigured settings as a cyber threat?*\r\n:::\r\n",
